OL,3,CPolice officer injured in hit-and-run
OL,5,FA police officer was injured in a hit-
OL,6,Fand-run incident after stopping a car
OL,7,Fin Halifax.
OL,9,FThe officer was in a patrol car with a
OL,10,Fcolleague when they saw a suspicious
OL,11,Fcar on Ovenden Way.
OL,13,FThey followed the car - a black
OL,14,FMercedes A180 - to Vegal Crescent,
OL,15,Fwhere it came to a stop.
OL,17,FAs the officer got out of the police
OL,18,Fcar, the Mercedes reversed into him
OL,19,Fbefore driving off.
