OL,3,CPolice officer injured in hit-and-run
OL,5,FIt was later abandoned on Moorside
OL,6,FGardens, at around 12.15pm on 7
OL,7,FNovember.
OL,9,FThe officer was taken to hospital with
OL,10,Fnon-life-threatening injuries.
OL,12,FDet Ch Insp Claire Smith, of
OL,13,FCalderdale District Police, said:
OL,14,F"This was clearly a dangerous incident
OL,15,Fwhere an officer, doing their job,
OL,16,Fended up injured and taken to hospital.
