OL,5,F"I would like to thank the local
OL,6,Fcommunity for the support and
OL,7,Fassistance with our enquiries this far
OL,8,Fas we continue to investigate and to
OL,9,Fthose who came to the officer's aid at
OL,10,Fthe time of the incident."
OL,12,FShe appealed for witnesses, and anyone
OL,13,Fwith CCTV footage, to come forward.
